{"type": "article", "id": 7944, "title": "Kazuya Koike 不沾水的雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-31T07:18:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234511ITiMk2rZ9bBVY5yO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t设计师 Kazuya Koike 设计了一款不沾水的雨伞，用来解决雨伞遇水后会有水柱流下，即使收起来也会打湿地板，或难以带在身上等问题。这款雨伞的伞面采用的是特殊的高密度织物材料，遇到水只需要轻轻一抖，水珠便会悉数落下，不留痕迹，便于携带。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234507dHEamM0Ui3QKvP4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345084Pxl2AaK7hSqvTYc.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234508KFwN2ry7deQpsvWl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345081TE5ryJS9iRXkfGI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234509QKoiflPW2TGwLdEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345093fWgueiploNsQ1nF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" da